Climate Change Capital Ltd. said it
joined a group of 30 experts and lobby groups urging the
 European Central Bank  to probe  Europe ’s investments in
“unsustainable” and high-pollution industries.  The investor made a statement by e-mail in  London  today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
